RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', AllDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', LspPingProtocolResults.LspPingUpCount AS 'LSP Up Count', LspPingProtocolResults.LspPingDownCount AS 'LSP Down Count', LspPingProtocolResults.TxEchoRequestCount AS 'Tx Echo Request Count', LspPingProtocolResults.RxEchoRequestCount AS 'Rx Echo Request Count', LspPingProtocolResults.TxEchoReplyCount AS 'Tx Echo Reply Count', LspPingProtocolResults.RxEchoReplyCount AS 'Rx Echo Reply Count' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, Port, LspPingProtocolConfig, LspPingProtocolResults, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LspPingProtocolConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND LspPingProtocolResults.ParentHnd = LspPingProtocolConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LspPingProtocolConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LspPingProtocolResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', LspPingProtocolResults.LspPingUpCount AS 'LSP Up Count', LspPingProtocolResults.LspPingDownCount AS 'LSP Down Count', LspPingProtocolResults.TxEchoRequestCount AS 'Tx Echo Request Count', LspPingProtocolResults.RxEchoRequestCount AS 'Rx Echo Request Count', LspPingProtocolResults.TxEchoReplyCount AS 'Tx Echo Reply Count', LspPingProtocolResults.RxEchoReplyCount AS 'Rx Echo Reply Count' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, ExternalDevicePort, LspPingProtocolConfig, LspPingProtocolResults, Port, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND LspPingProtocolConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND LspPingProtocolResults.ParentHnd = LspPingProtocolConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LspPingProtocolConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND LspPingProtocolResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
